{
  "texts": [
    "The interaction history H of user 𝑢 is fed into the LLM, so as to initialize the profile of surrogate user û.",
    "In the first round, û identifies a key attribute 𝑎 1 and uses external tools to fetch the related item set I 𝑎 1 û.",
    "For clarity and brevity, we omit the subscript û when the user is clear from the context.",
    "In the second round, û contrasts the preferences between I 𝑎 1 and H, selects another attribute 𝑎 2, and retrieves I 𝑎 2.",
    "Such iterative refinements continue until û is satisfied with the retrieved items, and outputs the final set I û ranked by preference."
  ]
}